'''''Space Mutiny''''' (izwi nka  '''''Mutiny in Space)''''' ni film yasohotse muri 1988 muri [[Afurika]] y'Epfo ikorwa na American [[:en:Space_opera|space opera]] [[:en:Action_film|action film]] filimi yerekeye ubwato bwitwa ''Southern Sun''<ref>Space Mutiny (Film) - TV Tropes</ref>''..'' Kuva ubwo iyi filime imaze guteza imbere umuco nyuma yo kugaragara mu gice kizwi cyane kuri televiziyo ''Mystery Science Theatre 3000'' <ref>Space Mutiny - Battlestar Wiki <nowiki>https://en.battlestarwiki.org</nowiki> › Space_Mutiny</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
''The Southern Sun'' ni ubwato bwibisekuruza, cyangwa ubwato bugenda mu kirere burimo abantu benshi<ref>Star Wars ripoff 'Space Mutiny' is peak '80s cheese in the best possible way (inverse.com)</ref>, intego yabo ni ugukoloniza isi nshya. Urugendo rwabwo kuva kwisi yambere (bivuze ko ari [[Isi]] ) bumaze ibisekuruza cumi na bitatu<ref>Space Mutiny - Daily Movies <nowiki>https://www.daily-movies.ch</nowiki> › space-...</ref>, kuburyo benshi mubayituye bavutse kandi bazapfa batigeze bakandagiza ikirenge hasi<ref>Space Mutiny | The Loft Cinema <nowiki>https://loftcinema.org</nowiki> › film › space-mutiny</ref>. Ibi ntibishimisha abanzi, Eliya Kalgan ( John Phillip ), wafatanije naba pirate binjira muri sisitemu ya Corona Borealis yegeranye n’umuyobozi mukuru w’ubwato MacPhearson ( James Ryan )<ref>Space Mutiny | Tucson Weekly <nowiki>https://www.tucsonweekly.com</nowiki> › space-mutiny › Film</ref>. Kalgan yateguye umugambi wo guhungabanya uburyo bwo kugendesha ubwato bwa Southern Sun no gukoresha Enforcers<ref>Space Mutiny - Hollywood Theatre <nowiki>https://hollywoodtheatre.org</nowiki> › events › space-mutiny</ref>, abapolisi b'ubwo bwato, kugira ngo bashimute ubwo bwato kandi babuyobore kuri ubu buryo. Kuri ubu, abatuye ''Southern Sun''' nta kundi byagenda uretse kwemera "ubuntu" bwe.<ref>Space Mutiny (1988) | Radio Times <nowiki>https://www.radiotimes.com</nowiki> › movie-guide › space-mut...</ref>

